<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fi">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>{{ domain if domain != "" else ansible_hostname }} – webserver-ansible</title>
  <style>
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #0d1117;
      color: #e6edf3;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .card {
      background: #161b22;
      border: 1px solid #30363d;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 2.5rem 3rem;
      max-width: 540px;
      width: 90%;
      text-align: center;
    }
    .badge {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 0.3rem 1rem;
      border-radius: 20px;
      font-size: 0.85rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
      {% if webserver == 'apache2' %}
      background: #c0392b22;
      color: #e74c3c;
      border: 1px solid #e74c3c44;
      {% else %}
      background: #27ae6022;
      color: #2ecc71;
      border: 1px solid #2ecc7144;
      {% endif %}
    }
    h1 { font-size: 1.6rem; margin-bottom: 0.75rem; }
    p  { color: #8b949e; line-height: 1.6; margin-bottom: 0.5rem; }
    .meta {
      margin-top: 2rem;
      padding-top: 1.5rem;
      border-top: 1px solid #30363d;
      font-size: 0.8rem;
      color: #484f58;
    }
    .meta a { color: #58a6ff; text-decoration: none; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="badge">{{ webserver }}</div>
    <h1>Asennus onnistui</h1>
    <p>Tämä sivu on asennettu automaattisesti Ansiblella.</p>
    <p>Webpalvelimena toimii <strong>{{ webserver }}</strong>
       {% if install_certbot == "yes" and domain != "" %}
       HTTPS-sertifikaatilla osoitteessa <strong>{{ domain }}</strong>.
       {% else %}
       ilman TLS-sertifikaattia.
       {% endif %}
    </p>
    <div class="meta">
      Asennettu koneelle <strong>{{ ansible_hostname }}</strong><br>
      Projekti: <a href="https://github.com/Havikki/webserver-ansible">github.com/Havikki/webserver-ansible</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
